{% set analyticsPageTitle = 'Start' %}
{% extends 'layout.nunjucks' %}

{% block header %}
<h1 class="local-header--title--question">Find a chlamydia test</h1>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
{% if errorMessage %}
<div class="error-summary">
  <h2 class="local-header--error error-summary-heading">
    {{ errorMessage }}
  </h2>
</div>
{% endif %}

<div class="reading-width">
  <p>The only way to know if you have <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/conditions/chlamydia/" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','ChlamydiaConditionsPage','WT.dl','121')">chlamydia</a> is to get tested.</p>

  <p>To get a chlamydia test you can:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>speak to your GP</li>
    <li>see a sexual health professional</li>
    <li>use a postal test kit</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>Use this service to find a sexual health professional or a chlamydia test kit near you.</strong></p>

  <div class="details--country details--country--england" id="england">
    <div class="details__header">
        <h2>England</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="details__content">
      <div class="reading-width">
        <p>If you’re in England, we can help you find a chlamydia test. We’ll ask you a few questions, and use your answers to show you where to get a test. It will take about 5 minutes.</p>
      
        <p>We may also use your answers to improve the NHS website. <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/aboutNHSChoices/aboutnhschoices/termsandconditions/Pages/Privacypolicy.aspx" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','NHSUKPrivacyPolicy','WT.dl','121')">Read the full NHS.UK privacy policy</a>.</p>

        <a href="{{ siteRoot }}/symptoms" class="button start-button" role="button" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','StartButton','WT.dl','121')">
          Find a chlamydia test
        </a>

        <p>If you would prefer to speak to someone, call the sexual health helpline on <a href="tel:03001237123" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','EnglandSexualHealthHelpline','WT.dl','121')">0300 123 7123</a>. Open Monday to Friday, 9am to 8pm.</p>

        <p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/call-charges" class="details__call-charges" target="_blank">Find out about call charges on GOV.UK.</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <details class="details--country details--country--scotland" id="scotland" role="group">
    <summary data-analytics="summary" role="button" aria-controls="details-content-1" aria-expanded="false" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','ScotlandInformation','WT.dl','121')">
      <span class="details__summary details__summary--country">Scotland</span>
    </summary>

    <div class="details__content" id="details-content-1" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="reading-width">
        <p>To find a chlamydia test in Scotland you can:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>use the <a href="http://www.sexualhealthscotland.co.uk/get-help/sexual-health-service-finder" target="_blank" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','ScotlandSexualHealthServiceFinder','WT.dl','121')">Sexual Health Scotland website</a></li>
          <li>call Sexual Health Scotland on <a href="tel:0800224488" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','ScotlandSexualHealthHelpline','WT.dl','121')">0800 22 44 88</a>
          <span class="details__opening-times">Monday to Friday, 8am to 10pm</span>
          <span class="details__opening-times">Saturday and Sunday, 9am to 5pm</span>
          <a href="https://www.gov.uk/call-charges" class="details__call-charges" target="_blank">Find out about call charges on GOV.UK</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="details--country details--country--wales" id="wales" role="group">
    <summary data-analytics="summary" role="button" aria-controls="details-content-2" aria-expanded="false" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','WalesInformation','WT.dl','121')">
      <span class="details__summary details__summary--country">Wales</span>
    </summary>

    <div class="details__content" id="details-content-2" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="reading-width">
        <p>To find a chlamydia test in Wales you can:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>use the <a href="https://www.nhsdirect.wales.nhs.uk/LocalServices/?s=SexualHealth" target="_blank" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','WalesNHSDirectWebsite','WT.dl','121')">NHS Direct Wales website</a></li>
          <li>call NHS Direct Wales on <a href="tel:08454647" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','WalesNHSDirectHelpline','WT.dl','121')">0845 46 47</a> (open 24 hours)
          <a href="https://www.gov.uk/call-charges" class="details__call-charges" target="_blank">Find out about call charges on GOV.UK</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>

  <details class="details--country details--country--northern" id="northern" role="group">
    <summary data-analytics="summary" role="button" aria-controls="details-content-3" aria-expanded="false" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','NorthernIrelandInformation','WT.dl','121')">
      <span class="details__summary details__summary--country">Northern Ireland</span>
    </summary>

    <div class="details__content" id="details-content-3" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="reading-width">
        <p>To find a chlamydia test in Northern Ireland you can:</p>

        <ul>
          <li>use the <a href="https://sexualhealthni.info/chlamydia" target="_blank" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','NorthernIrelandSexualHealthWebsite','WT.dl','121')">Sexual Health NI website</a></li>
          <li>call the Family Planning Association sexual health helpline on <a href="tel:03451228687" onclick="DCSMultiTrack('DCSext.Chlamydia','NorthernIrelandSexualHealthHelpline','WT.dl','121')">0345 122 8687</a>
          <span class="details__opening-times">Monday to Friday, 9am to 5pm (closed on bank holidays)</span>
          <a href="https://www.gov.uk/call-charges" class="details__call-charges" target="_blank">Find out about call charges on GOV.UK</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </details>

</div>

{% endblock %}
